title: rs1663689 interchromosomally regulates ADGRG6 and modulates the malignant progression of lung cancer
description: Our studies demonstrated a nontraditional trans-effect of a genetic variant and suggest a novel personalized treatment strategy for lung cancer patients harboring the T/T genotype at rs1663689.
